<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3699465>
    dc:description "Figure 1. Species groups of Southeast Asian Nigidius species based on ocular canthus shape. 1a) Nigidius obesus group. 1b) cornutus group. 1c) distinctus group. 1d) laevicollis group." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3699465/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3699467>
    dc:description "Figure 2. Nigidius obesus Parry, lectotype male, with labels (inset)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3699467/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3699469>
    dc:description "Figures 3–4. Nigidius dawnae Gravely. 3) Major male, dorsal habitus. 4) Lectotype male with labels." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3699469/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3699471>
    dc:description "Figure 5. Nigidius gravelyi Paulsen, n. sp., holotype male, with labels (inset)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3699471/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3699473>
    dc:description "Figures 6–7. Nigidius helleri Boileau. 6) Major male, dorsal habitus. 7) Holotype male with labels. Photo courtesy of Antoine Mantilleri, MNHN." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3699473/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

